{"tid":1882753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"挑戰危機撚！泰國4月擬推免簽吸陸客救觀光","createTime":"2020-02-16T12:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T12:05:56.000Z","uid":31215,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"1ef71c48a369777716314bd03f59b7b27d2a58ae","tid":1882753,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T12:40:20.000Z","msg":"泰國曼谷郵報報導，觀光官員再次提議提供中國大陸公民免簽證入境，作為振興觀光業計畫的一部分。觀光和體育部長皮帕（Phiphat Ratchakitprakarn）表示，本月1日至9日間國際旅客人次比去年同期降低43.4%，其中陸客人數暴跌86.6%。<br />\n<br />\n皮帕表示，大陸觀光客人數本月很可能下降90%，但如果有效遏制疫情，且大陸政府若能在3月底前解除旅遊禁令，陸客很可能會在4月潑水節期間回流。他也說，對中國大陸和印度2個觀光業主要市場推行的免簽政策，是紓解機場旅客擁擠狀況的必要措施。<br />\n<br />\n皮帕說：「我們打算在4月重新提交免簽政策給內閣，因為泰國落地簽證2000泰銖免除方案將在4月30日結束，但前提是中國當局必須先控制疫情。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6786948/article-無懼疫情-泰國4月擬推免簽吸陸客救觀光/?ismobile=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6786948%2Farticle-%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B4%E6%9C%88%E6%93%AC%E6%8E%A8%E5%85%8D%E7%B0%BD%E5%90%B8%E9%99%B8%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%91%E8%A7%80%E5%85%89%2F%3Fismobile%3Dtrue&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=6c30d59c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6786948/article-無懼疫情-泰國4月擬推免簽吸陸客救觀光/?ismobile=true</a><br />\n<br />\n泰國政府睇唔起隻病<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜都唔封唔搞，咁耐都感染唔到100人係廢啲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1c21f72c53b65940f485e62ae3d5547ea39808","tid":1882753,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T12:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea75a086bc7778a506695cd11ab6fad1cef03d94","tid":1882753,"uid":36901,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T12:43:24.000Z","msg":"花式自殺"},{"pid":"94f2000da7fb